ComicInfo.Summary:
Things get worse for the little band of Irish soldiers entering Hitler’s Third Reich, as the German army turns out to have plenty of fight left in it. A battle in the deep woods leaves our heroes lost and scattered- and that’s when one of them decides to settle an old score. Tensions from Ireland’s bloody past come to a head, in part two of Our Wild Geese Go, by Garth Ennis and Tomas Aira. Available with Regular & Wraparound Covers by Tomas Aria, and Good Girl Nose Art & Battle Damage Retailer Incentive Covers by Matt Martin.
